                        <button data-tab="phrases" class="tab-btn py-3 px-4 sm:px-6 font-semibold text-gray-600 rounded-t-lg border-b-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-200 transition"><span class="icon">ğŸ’¬</span>á€¡á€á€¯á€¶á€¸á€¡á€”á€¾á€¯á€”á€ºá€¸á€™á€»á€¬á€¸</button>
